        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "ments can make three potential plays: (a) win on cost and scale, (b) find a differentiated niche, and (c) go beyond the core of automotive supply into new business models. Those starting with businesses that today are driven heavily by differentiating performance innovation for which customers are willing to pay more face a core choice whether to remain traditional suppliers and (d)",
